  "id": "RAW_eb2530",
  "title": "GLM-4.5 编码套餐：20 元包月，人人畅享全球顶级 Claude Code 编码体验",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&mid=2247491892&idx=1&sn=dc9ef5b38b45a828c243ef2ac3f35ea8",
  "date": "2025-09-01 10:38:00",
  "author": "智谱",
  "siteName": "智谱",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"display: inline-block;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mf0zaepvdgz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-backh=\"247\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4271604938271605\" data-type=\"jpg\" data-w=\"1620\" style=\"width: 100%;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b38977c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUBWAWibiaa4jespJjIiaT7yzicIkJ66YhfA39FHBepCM0DYk8OYVb1fsnk22WW1iakibCO3ljnL8gAf3iblm7U1zcmiaqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span><span leaf=\"\">过去一段时间，越来越多开发者在真实编码任务中开始采用 GLM-4.5。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">在前端开发、跨文件修改、全栈项目构建等典型场景中，GLM-4.5 展现出稳定、实用的表现，逐步成为不少用户的主要编程助手。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">根据反馈，其解决实际问题的能力已接近 Claude Sonnet 4。在多个开源评测中，GLM-4.5 也与国际主流模型保持同等竞争力：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:20px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:34px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">WebDev Arena</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：与全球领先模型并列第二；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);\">SWE-bench Verified</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">：性能优于 &nbsp;Gemini-2.5-Pro 和 GPT-4.1；</span></span></li>\n   <li><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">BFCL v4 基准</span>：全球第一，超过 Claude Opus 4.1，成本仅为其 1.5%。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">为进一步降低 AI 编码工具的使用门槛，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">我们正式推出限时 Claude Code 专属套餐「GLM Coding P</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">lan</span></span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">」——月费低至 20 元</span>，让更多用户以合理成本使用高质量的代码生成能力。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">在真实 Agentic Coding 场景中展现卓越性能</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">为评估模型的 Agentic Coding 能力，我们构建了 CC-Bench 评测体系，并将 GLM-4.5 与 Claude Sonnet 4、DeepSeek-V3.1、Kimi-K2 和 Qwen3-Coder-480B 在</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">覆盖六大开发领域的</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;52 个实际编程任务上进行了对比。所有模型在相同环境中测试，确保公平性。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mf0mx1m91ox4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100008236\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4953125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"286\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=530ca1cb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUBWAWibiaa4jfgJumJ5cxVFfttRicDGqAaSsB1zpvpI0WEvlEFTHbLib4VUC4G6nY9seicSEffKOeGHAC73POXBok6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:start;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">CC-Bench评测体系：</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mdmv4u3pkhj\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/zai-org/CC-Bench-trajectories\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/zai-org/CC-Bench-trajectories</a></span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">结果显示，GLM-4.5 在开源模型中表现优异，尤其在任务完成效果和工具调用可靠性方面。</span><span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); margin: 0px 0px 4px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; word-break: break-all; min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">GLM-4.5 在编码性能方面接近&nbsp;</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Claude Sonnet 4，但价格仅为后者的 1/7，性价比优势显著，为开发者提供高性价比选择。</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">限时体验，低门槛开启高效编程</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">自<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;9 月 1 日</span>起，我们推出「GLM Coding P</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">lan</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">」限时套餐，</span><span leaf=\"\">该套餐适用于智谱最新旗舰模型 GLM-4.5 及 GLM-4.5-Air</span><span leaf=\"\">。用户可通过扫描活动海报二维码，或者登录</span><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">智谱开放平台<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;bigmodel.cn</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">，</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\">直接购买并获取详细使用攻略。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span data-eleid=\"16\"><span data-eleid=\"16\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 15px; line-height: 26px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); margin: 0px 0px 4px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; word-break: break-all; min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;text-only&quot;,&quot;data-eleid&quot;:&quot;16&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">首期主推 Claude Code，</span></span><span leaf=\"\">未来将拓展到更多 Coding 工具。目前，GLM-4.5 已接入包括 Claude Code、Cline、Gemini CLI、Grok CLI、CodeGeeX、Kilo Code、Roo Code、Trae 在内的多款主流编程工具，全面支持日常开发流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangS